{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioItem"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","title":"OUDSRadioItem","roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioItem"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents13OUDSRadioItemV"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To"}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(isOn:label:additionalLabel:helper:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/body"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","title":"Default Implementations"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some radios components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a radio with only an indicator, prefer instead "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Layouts","level":2,"text":"Layouts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reversed"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing radio indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2,"text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The radio indicator has two available states:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"text":": the radio is filled with a filled circle, the user has made the action to select the radio","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the radio is empty, does not contain anything, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the radio"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2,"text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The radio can be also outlined in some cases."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom radio trait."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","level":2,"text":"Forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"can be used outside a dedicated picker, thus it does not need any tag and associated type.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, and an additional label but without text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing radio with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  label: \"Rescue from this world!\",","                  helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                  isReversed: true,","                  isError: true,","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Rescue from this world!\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related radio as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Kaboom!\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Kaboom!\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/90c467-radio-button","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","level":3,"text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","level":3,"text":"Orange Business Tools"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_OrangeBusinessTools","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Inverse","level":3,"text":"Orange Inverse"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioItem_OrangeInverse"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","level":3,"text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3,"text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Wireframe","type":"image"}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.1.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"name":"Version"},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Since"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradioitem"]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor"